  "description": "The Wizard of Oz but it's set in a senior citizen retirement home. Dorothy just wants to go home. Scarecrow has dementia. Tinman has stiff joints and heart problems. Lion has agoraphobia. \"Neil is an incredibly gifted performer, transitioning between a dozen distinct characters, giving each one life and personality\" ★★★★★",
